## The Sensor-to-Intelligence Pipeline

```
SONAR ARRAY (I2C/SPI)
    → flux-isa-mini (Cortex-M4, validates raw readings)
        → flux-isa-std (RPi, compiles CSP, local quality gate)
            → flux-isa-edge (Jetson Xavier, async pipelines, PLATO sync)
                → flux-isa-thor (Jetson Thor, GPU batch solve, fleet coordination)
                    → PLATO (persistent verified knowledge)
```

Every tier compiles constraints before execution. Wrong is a compilation error at every level.

